data.description: 2.75% assumable VA loan! Discover an exceptional opportunity in Marysville, where this stunning  4-bedroom, 1-bathroom home awaits. This home has the best of both worlds.  It's completely updated but has kept it's original charm. Situated on a generous lot of nearly a quarter-acre, this property boasts a host of desirable features, including a fully fenced backyard, pond, garden space,  room for all your parking needs, a 2-car garage, beautiful natural hardwood floors, and a brand-new kitchen. The primary bedroom upstairs creates a quiet sanctuary to unwind from the day.  All of this comes without the encumbrance of a HOA, making this an attractive prospect for those who value space, convenience, individuality,and room for all of your toys!
